gb(246, 98, 0);"></div></div></div><div style="margin: 0px 1px; height: 1px; overflow: hidden; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style="height: 1px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 1px; background-color: rgb(249, 150, 85);"><div style="height: 1px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 1px; background-color: rgb(247, 108, 16);"><div style="height: 1px; overflow: hidden; margin: 0px 1px; background-color: rgb(246, 98, 0);"></div></div></div></div></div></div><p>There a lots of clever ways to enhance your chat in Habbo - Learn them all, or just a couple, but they''re all here in one handy list just for you!</p><ul><li>(hold shift when pressing enter) Shout loudly and in <b>bold</b></li><li><b>:whisper &lt;username&gt;</b> Whisper privately to username</li><li><b>:mutepets</b> Ignore pet chats</li><li><b>:mutebots</b> Ignore bot chats</li><li><b>o/</b> or <b>_o/</b> Wave</li><li><b>:idle</b> Go to sleep</li><li><b>_b</b> Thumbs up</li><li><b>:sign &lt;number 0-10&gt;</b> Show a number sign</li><li><b>:sign &lt;number 11-17&gt;</b> Show a special sign</li><li><b>:pickall</b> Pick all your furniture up from the room</li><li><b>:pickallbc</b> Pick all builders club furniture up from the room</li><li><b>:ejectall</b> Eject all furniture in a group room</li><li><b>:sit</b> Sit down</li><li><b>:stand</b> Stand up</li></ul><h2>For Habbo Club members only</h2><ul><li><b>:kiss</b> Blow kiss</li><li><b>:D</b> or <b>;D</b> Laugh</li><li><b>:chooser</b> Open the user chooser tool</li><li><b>:furni</b> Open the furniture chooser tool</li><li><b>:kick &lt;username&gt;</b> Kick username from room if you are admin</li><li><b>:kickall</b> Kick everybody from the room if you are admin</li></ul><h2>For Builders Club members only</h2><ul><li><b>:floor</b> Edit the floor plan</li><li><b>:bcfloor</b> Edit the floor plan</li></ul><h2>Special characters with alt-codes!</h2><p>For extra fun you can trigger special characters by holding down the alt-key on your keyboard and entering the following codes on the numeric keyboard!</p><img src="http://habboo-a.akamaihd.net/c_images/habbopages/chat_altcodes.png" height="295" hspace="1" vspace="1"/>
